    dc:description "FIGURES 1–11. Scirtothrips quercus sp.n. (1) Whole body, female; (2) Whole body, male; (3) Head–metanotum, female; (4) Head–metanotum, male; (5) Tergites VII–X, female; (6) Tergites VIII–X with drepanae, male; (7) Tergites III–VI, female; (8); Sternites III–VIII, female; (9) Forewing, female; (10) Antenna, female; (11) Antenna, male." ;
